title: How to Get Out of Your Comfort Zone
itunes:title: How to Get Out of Your Comfort Zone
description:
In this week's episode, Brooke and Danielle are reunited after spring break! Let's talk about getting out of your comfort zone, times we have had to push ourselves, dating, and some more spring break recaps!

Go to https://www.daily-harvest.com and enter promo code galsonthego to get three cups FREE in your first box!

You can check out our channels on YouTube:

Brooke Miccio

Danielle Carolan

For business inquiries email brookeanddaniellepodcast@gmail.com with “Gals On the Go Podcast” in the subject! Follow us on Instagram and Twitter to be involved in the next episode’s Q&A: @daniellecarolan @brookemiccio Talk to you guys next Wednesday and for the next episode!

Follow @galsonthegopodcast on Instagram to submit your own questions for next week’s episode, get involved, and more!
